description: Try our easy to follow Asian Beef Tacos recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Asian Beef Tacos Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Build the taco using the cabbage and carrot mix, slices of avocado, the marinated beef and top with spicy mayonnaise and green onions. Serve with lime wedges.
